code: /**  * Whether the user has any sessions.  */ boolean hasSessions().

code: /**  * Look up the session for the given id.  * @param sessionId the session id  * @return the matching session, or {@code null} if none found  */ @Nullable SimpSession getSession(String sessionId).

code: /**  * Return the sessions for the user.  * The returned set is a copy and will never be modified.  * @return a set of session ids, or an empty set if none  */ Set<SimpSession> getSessions().
